{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/studio-theme-adding-vertical-thumbnails-and-arrows-to-the-product-page-images","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1710,"date":"2022-10-25T09:57:30","date_gmt":"2022-10-25T09:57:30","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1710"},"modified":"2022-10-25T11:05:27","modified_gmt":"2022-10-25T11:05:27","slug":"studio-theme-adding-vertical-thumbnails-and-arrows-to-the-product-page-images","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/studio-theme-adding-vertical-thumbnails-and-arrows-to-the-product-page-images/","title":{"rendered":"Studio theme: vertical thumbnails with arrows on product pages [no apps]"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>The Studio theme is a theme popularly used for artists. When selling artistic products it&#8217;s common practice to try and make the best of the available space, no matter how small it is, by using thumbnails to showcase their variety. The default horizontal layout of the Studio theme’s might not be the best for such a thing however as your clients might have a hard time getting a good view of your product&#8217;s finer details.<br><br>This can be discouraging for your clients as browsing though your store might turn into a chore, and worst case scenario they&#8217;ll even give up on a purchase. Using this vertical scheme for product thumbnails, arrows for scrolling included, your clients will have an easier time looking at your products. <br><br>As well as vertical thumbnails, there&#8217;s other important elements to the UX that the Studio theme lacks, for example:<br><br>&#8211; image arrows;<br>&#8211; looping products images;<br>&#8211; vertical thumbnails;<br>&#8211; sync swatches when images change (and the other way around).<br>&#8211; dots; <br><br>Such functionalities can certainly improve a store, but the time and effort required to implement them can be a big discouragement for owners of a Studio theme store. Long and complicated discussions with developers, questionable results and steep costs are just some of the problems that frequently arises.<br><br>Today I&#8217;ll show how to easily add vertical thumbnails and more to your Studio theme, simply by pasting code already written and tested by certified Shopify partners with rich experience in coding and modifying themes.<br><br>And above all else, customizations <strong>will not be overwritten</strong>! So if you already modified your theme code before, all your changes will still be there after you&#8217;re done. <br><br><a href=\"https://studio-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here is a live preview of what the end result will look like.</a> (Password: <strong>123</strong>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-theme\">Making a backup of your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-downloading-the-files\">Downloading the files</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/shop/studio-theme-slider-pro\"><strong>Download </strong>the files by clicking here.</a> (<a href=\"https://studio-password-is-123.myshopify.com/products/flex-bag\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">live preview</a>)</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-step-1-inserting-the-top-code\">Step 1: inserting the &#8220;top&#8221; code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Starting from your Shopify admin, navigate to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>> <strong>Actions </strong>> <strong>Edit Code</strong>.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1271\" height=\"423\" class=\"wp-image-1844\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1.png\" alt=\"Opening the code editor from the Shopify store admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1.png 1271w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1-850x283.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1-1200x399.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-1-768x256.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1271px) 100vw, 1271px\" /><br></li><li>On the search bar type the following:<br><br><strong>main-product.liquid</strong><br><br>This will lead to the relevant file you&#8217;ll then click. <br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"872\" height=\"632\" class=\"wp-image-1562\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1.jpg 872w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1-850x616.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-1-768x557.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 872px) 100vw, 872px\" /></li><li>Inside the .zip you downloaded, you&#8217;ll find a file called <strong>top.txt</strong>. Copy all of the code within.</li><li>Paste the code at the start of the <strong>main-product.liquid</strong> file, as shown in the image. <br><br>Before:<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1092\" height=\"642\" class=\"wp-image-1566\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2.jpg 1092w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2-850x500.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-2-768x452.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1092px) 100vw, 1092px\" /><br><br>After:<br><br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1171\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1817\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-4.png 1171w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-4-850x441.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-4-768x399.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1171px) 100vw, 1171px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 2: inserting the &#8220;bottom&#8221; code</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Still in the same &#8220;main-product.liquid&#8221; file, press CTRL + F (or CMD + F on Mac) and search for:<br><br><strong>{% schema</strong><br><br>Make sure there is a space after the %.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1277\" height=\"733\" class=\"wp-image-1568\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4.jpg 1277w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-850x488.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-1200x689.jpg 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-4-768x441.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1277px) 100vw, 1277px\" /><br></li><li>Then delete everything <strong>below </strong>the {% schema %} line, that includes the {% schema %}.<strong> </strong><br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1134\" height=\"730\" class=\"wp-image-1570\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5.jpg 1134w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-850x547.jpg 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/dawn-5-768x494.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1134px) 100vw, 1134px\" /></li><li>In the .zip you downloaded, there is a file called <strong>bottom.txt</strong>. <br><br>Copy the code inside it and then paste it at the very end of the file.<br><br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"580\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5-1200x580.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1819\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5-1200x580.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5-850x411.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5-768x371.png 768w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-5.png 1367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>And it&#8217;s done! </li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-final-step-slider-activation-and-customization\">Final step: slider activation and customization</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify admin, go to <strong>Online Store</strong> > <strong>Themes </strong>><strong>Customize</strong>. Select the theme to which you just added the code.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1275\" height=\"328\" class=\"wp-image-1847\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-2.png\" alt=\"Opening theme customization from Shopify store admin\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-2.png 1275w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-2-850x219.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-2-1200x309.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-2-768x198.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1275px) 100vw, 1275px\" /><br></li><li>Near the top, open the dropdown menu and select <strong>Products</strong>> <strong>default product</strong>. <br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"851\" height=\"556\" class=\"wp-image-1852\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-3.png\" alt=\"Opening product information on theme customization page\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-3.png 851w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-3-768x502.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 851px) 100vw, 851px\" /><br></li><li>Once the page loads, click on <strong>Product Information</strong> to the left.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"835\" height=\"589\" class=\"wp-image-1854\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-4.png\" alt=\"Opening product information on side menu\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-4.png 835w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/Screenshot-studio-4-768x542.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 835px) 100vw, 835px\" /><br></li><li>Scroll down to the <strong>Media </strong>section and activate your preferred option. For this tutorial, we&#8217;ll go for vertical thumbnails:<br><br></li></ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"418\" height=\"528\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/image-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1821\"/></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-it-didn-t-go-as-intended-and-i-m-not-sure-why\">It didn&#8217;t go as intended and I&#8217;m not sure why</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>No worries at all! We&#8217;ll gladly help you out. <br><br>Please send us an email to <strong>ezfycode@gmail.com</strong> containing your website URL and on the same day we&#8217;ll get back to you, ready to assist you with the installation.</p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>By following this tutorial you&#8217;ll learn how to add vertical scrolling for thumbnails in your Studio theme, as well as arrows for scrolling.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":1836,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","stic